{
  "stem": "7938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were kapos and everybody, soldiers all around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The first group went to the showers, and they had some towels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The second group didn't have a towel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When somebody asked for a towel, he got hit so that he didn't get out anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they kept us wet outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was-- it was a cold November day already, or late October, whatever-- November.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were all-- we were all cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We huddled together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Without any clothes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Completely naked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, finally, [INAUDIBLE] when a group came together already, when there was enough people, they put us-- they took us to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were sitting-- first of all, they didn't give any clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were sitting there on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then came another group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, finally, there was not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not enough room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- so they told us, we will show you that we will have room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put people-- they told people to lie down, one onto another one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he put one in between, somebody on the top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he jumped on him, and then he pushed him in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he showed us that they can do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, finally, they filled up the room and they started giving us some undershirt, whatever they gave us, and the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the uniforms-- of course, nobody asked already whether it's big enough or small enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody took what he could, and then later, among themselves, they tried to-- and the next day, we came out on the-- they didn't take us to any work during these times.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed about-- altogether, until we left, about six days, I think, or five or six days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we went every day out, and we saw the people who were working there.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
